.
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1389] fixed make_docs.nu for Nu v0.93.0
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1383] upgraded lefthook, shiki, and vuepress plugins
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1379] refreshed command docs for Nu v0.93
.
