[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1381] fixed a broken link to plugin protocol reference
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1380] clarified that 
``plugin use``
 is not needed in the config file
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1368] provided release notes for 0.93.0
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1367] documented the plugin management overhaul - new commands and new file format
, along with documentation for other features.
