[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1375] nearly finished 0.93.0 release notes
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1373] edited 
``0.93.0``
 release notes
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1374] provided release notes for Polars plugin and dataframes deprecation
.
tesujimath 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1372] added a reference to Nu Plugin Tracer in the Nushell Book
.
